{"tid":706764,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國真係一個好屈機既國家","createTime":"2018-06-18T07:10:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T16:40:04.000Z","uid":19552,"like":50,"dislike":346,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"0f95a8f9ebc88e07437ededac85fc929a1f5c5fb","tid":706764,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T07:10:51.000Z","msg":"運動勁 足球試過世界盃拎第四 亞洲杯又亞軍 又有球員踢過偉大既曼聯仲拎埋歐聯 <br />\r\n冬奧項目果d又叻 東亞籃球黎講又算係一線 <br />\r\n傳統奧運項目好似游水更加唔洗講啦 傳統文化又保留得好 <br />\r\n野食又好味 部隊鍋, 韓燒同埋泡菜真係屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n科技無得輸啦 三星一間贏哂 出街有邊個唔係用S9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n都唔洗數LG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> LG都有出部G6 我自己都用緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n音樂更加係世界頂尖 big gang 既g-danger, 少時既sunny哩D真係迷死人 <br />\r\n電視一套 薔薇色的戀人們 都玩哂啦 已經唔洗講 青鳥之家同我的愛屬於你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n電影韓國不嬲都係亞洲最強 唔洗多講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n綜藝娛樂 RUNNING MAN風靡全球 少男少女都鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n就連打aoc呀，韓國都係勁到比人禁用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n圍棋又係首屈一指，你見高永夏勁過進滕光多多聲就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n打機仲勁添 starcraft 勁,蟲神NesTea出哂名屈機, <br />\r\nlol又勁 一個pawn都打爆哂班垃圾鬼佬同台仔大陸佬 已經唔洗數faker <br />\r\n兩隻最主流既遊戲都係韓仔玩哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打機勁 娛樂勁 運動勁 乜都勁 <br />\r\n就連波台改歌都係用kpop你就知韓國沙pop啦 <br />\r\n好心你班反韓高登仔面對現實啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n<br />\r\n仲有韓國燒酒又係數一數二好飲既酒, 乜春野女兒紅sake vodka真係得啖笑 <br />\r\n而且韓國上網速度蟬聯左幾年世界第一 韓國啤仲好飲過德啤 <br />\r\n<br />\r\n就連倫敦一哥熱刺都要高價收購son黎衝擊英超呀 <br />\r\n真係唔知你班高登仔仲反乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n[fuck] [fuck] [fuck] [fuck] [fuck] [fuck] [fuck] [fuck] [fuck]<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://www.state.gov/img/11/44705/south_korea_flag_454_1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Fimg%2F11%2F44705%2Fsouth_korea_flag_454_1.gif&h=4c6c81a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcee823e612f534dbb10b7dc949963f946cabc81","tid":706764,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T07:12:24.000Z","msg":"韓國燒酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7686eb138a40a2a8c9a8f263168e0035a8bd1626","tid":706764,"uid":82304,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T07:12:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/151255_491d1806b07ed7bc20903fc9477f5012.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F18%2F151255_491d1806b07